channel.title: Help with a few things?
channel.description:
I'm using TrisidiaX V3.
How do I make the Comp Cape not need 99/120 dung and 99 pking to get it but you need all other skills 99.
How do I make funpk into multi or a multi pking area
when im making a custom webclient and my own cache do i upload my cache to dropbox and put it in client.java and gui.java

item.title: Help with a few things?
item.dc:creator: @3lv3n_snip3r 3lv3n snip3r
item.description:
@3lv3n_snip3r wrote:

Are Dungeoneering the and pking skills the last 2 skills? If so, just go to the last skill you want it to be. I could help you out a little more if you provided us with what you’ve tried so far.

For the FunPk, go into your Player class and find ‘inMulti()’, just put the coordinates in there.

For the cache downloading, upload your cache to the public link of Dropbox. Then, in your CacheDownloader class, put the link that it gives you where ever the previous link was at.
